column5: I had this sent to me by my godfather,and I thought I would share with you all.Dont laugh at me ok.  The scene with me and my grandfather ,is  a classic, and dear to my heart. OH ,CAN YOU PICK OUT MEMART?
First pic is  of my grand parent,pops side.
2nd is me Mudder
3rd MY POP.I now know where I got my good looks from.
I had a feeling that someone was going to be wearing icing. Thanks for sharing.
